{"id":14881384,"mediaExerciseId":"5d30dcde-6976-4d8b-a05c-d415bf4821ea","exerciseName":"2","chapterName":"13","chapterTitle":"Return, Risk, and The Security Market Line","groupId":612371,"groupTitle":"Work The Web","isPremium":true,"sectionName":"13.6","sectionTitle":"Systematic Risk and Beta","pageNumber":436,"solutions":[{"id":5998874,"modifiedOn":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000000","steps":[{"columns":[{"text":"We are asked to determine the company's growth rate in this exercise.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":28,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/09/9d4920ff184d75ec8b9a9ecb78a1779c/bd23d40ef39fe84aeced9d424cc638c0/lateximg_large.png","width":931},"regular":{"height":15,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/09/9d4920ff184d75ec8b9a9ecb78a1779c/bd23d40ef39fe84aeced9d424cc638c0/lateximg.png","width":466}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":1},{"columns":[{"text":"Allow me to assist you in completing this exercise.\n\nBegin by searching for the company indicated in this exercise on finance.yahoo.com. The website will show the company's statistics.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":103,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/09/9d4920ff184d75ec8b9a9ecb78a1779c/2b455d1e0d035d7454be44ef8aafac0f/lateximg_large.png","width":1077},"regular":{"height":52,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/09/9d4920ff184d75ec8b9a9ecb78a1779c/2b455d1e0d035d7454be44ef8aafac0f/lateximg.png","width":539}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":2},{"columns":[{"text":"Next, let us determine the company's growth rate that analysts project. The growth rate is the percentage increase in the value of a portfolio over a certain period. The growth rate is useful in determining the worth of security because it enables investors to see how investment security performs over time.\n","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":174,"